---
import PortalLayout from "../layouts/PortalLayout.astro";
---

<PortalLayout title="Pipelines">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Pipelines</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-10">Automated tools organized by department.</p>

    <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         PRE-SALE — PROPOSAL GENERATOR — amber
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Pre-Sale</span>
        <div class="flex-1 border-t border-amber-200"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 p-8 mb-6 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1">Website Migration Proposal</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-6">Enter the client's current site URL. Runs a 5-source audit and generates the full Website Modernization Proposal (Google Doc). This is a sales tool — no registry entry is created. When the sale closes, use the Migration Pipeline below.</p>
        <form id="proposal-form" class="space-y-4">
          <input type="url" id="site-url" required placeholder="https://clientsite.com"
            class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-stone-800 placeholder-stone-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-300 text-base" />
          <button type="submit" id="proposal-btn"
            class="w-full bg-amber-200 hover:bg-amber-300 text-amber-900 font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed">
            Generate Proposal
          </button>
        </form>
        <div id="proposal-status" class="hidden mt-5">
          <div id="proposal-spinner" class="hidden flex items-center gap-3 text-stone-600 text-sm">
            <svg class="animate-spin h-4 w-4 shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle class="opacity-25" cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"></circle><path class="opacity-75" fill="currentColor" d="M4 12a8 8 0 018-8v8z"></path></svg>
            <span>Auditing site and building proposal — 2–4 minutes…</span>
          </div>
          <div id="proposal-result" class="hidden p-5 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl space-y-2">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-green-800">Proposal ready!</p>
            <a id="proposal-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block text-green-700 underline font-medium text-sm">Open Proposal →</a>
            <p class="text-xs text-stone-500 pt-1">When the sale closes, start Phase 1 in the Migration Pipeline below.</p>
          </div>
          <div id="proposal-error" class="hidden p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-red-800 mb-1">Error</p>
            <p id="proposal-error-text" class="text-sm text-red-700 font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap"></p>
          </div>
          <div id="proposal-challenge" class="hidden p-6 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-300 rounded-xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">Cloudflare Verification Required</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-stone-600 mb-3">This site requires human verification. Click the CAPTCHA checkbox in the image below to proceed.</p>
            <div class="relative inline-block cursor-pointer border border-stone-300 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
              <img id="challenge-img" src="" alt="Cloudflare challenge" class="max-w-full" style="max-height: 500px;" />
            </div>
            <div class="mt-3 flex gap-3">
              <button id="challenge-refresh" class="text-xs text-amber-700 underline hover:text-amber-900">Refresh Screenshot</button>
              <button id="challenge-dismiss" class="text-xs text-red-600 underline hover:text-red-800">Skip (abort proposal)</button>
            </div>
            <p id="challenge-status-text" class="text-xs text-stone-500 mt-2">Click on the checkbox in the image above.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div><!-- end Pre-Sale -->

    <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         WEBSITE MIGRATION — rose — 9 phases
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-rose-100 text-rose-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Website Migration</span>
        <div class="flex-1 border-t border-rose-200"></div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-4 -mt-2">The Transformation System — 9 phases, enforced in order. Clone the existing site to SMP stack.</p>

      <!-- How This Works -->
      <div class="bg-rose-50 border border-rose-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6 text-xs text-stone-600 space-y-2">
        <p class="font-bold text-rose-800 text-sm">How the migration pipeline works</p>
        <ol class="list-decimal ml-4 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Start a project</strong> — use Phase 1 below to create the infrastructure (automated)</li>
          <li><strong>Work through each phase</strong> — SSH into Bethel, <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">cd ~/Sites/&lt;slug&gt; && claude</code>, follow the instructions for the current phase</li>
          <li><strong>Verify your work</strong> — each phase has a green checklist at the bottom. Check every item.</li>
          <li><strong>Advance</strong> — use the Phase Tracker above to click "Mark Phase Complete &amp; Advance"</li>
          <li><strong>Repeat</strong> — the tracker shows your current phase. Work through it, verify, advance. Phase 7 (QA) runs automated scans via the tracker.</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="text-stone-500">Phases are enforced in order — you cannot skip ahead. If a phase fails, fix the issues before advancing.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase tracker per project -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-rose-200 p-6 mb-6 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-stone-800 mb-3">Project Phase Tracker</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <select id="mig-tracker-project"
            class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-stone-800 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-rose-300 bg-white text-sm">
            <option value="">Select a migration project…</option>
          </select>
          <div id="mig-tracker" class="hidden">
            <div id="mig-phase-bar" class="flex gap-1 mb-4"></div>
            <div id="mig-phase-detail" class="text-sm text-stone-600 mb-4"></div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <button id="mig-advance-btn"
                class="bg-rose-200 hover:bg-rose-300 text-rose-900 font-semibold py-2 px-5 rounded-lg transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed text-sm">
                Mark Phase Complete &amp; Advance
              </button>
              <button id="mig-qa-btn"
                class="hidden bg-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-800 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-5 rounded-lg transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed text-sm">
                Run Pre-Launch QA (8 scans)
              </button>
            </div>
            <div id="mig-advance-msg" class="hidden mt-3 p-3 rounded-lg text-sm"></div>
            <!-- QA results -->
            <div id="qa-status" class="hidden mt-5">
              <div id="qa-spinner" class="hidden flex items-center gap-3 text-stone-600 text-sm">
                <svg class="animate-spin h-4 w-4 shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle class="opacity-25" cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"></circle><path class="opacity-75" fill="currentColor" d="M4 12a8 8 0 018-8v8z"></path></svg>
                <span>Running 8 scans + build gate…</span>
              </div>
              <div id="qa-result" class="hidden">
                <div id="qa-summary" class="mb-4 p-4 rounded-lg text-sm font-semibold"></div>
                <div id="qa-scans" class="space-y-3"></div>
              </div>
              <div id="qa-error" class="hidden p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-red-800 mb-1">Error</p>
                <p id="qa-error-text" class="text-sm text-red-700 font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap"></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 1: Initiate Build (Bootstrap) -->
      <div class="bg-rose-50 rounded-2xl border border-rose-200 p-8 mb-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-rose-700 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">1</span>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Phase 1 — Infrastructure</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-rose-700 bg-rose-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">AUTOMATED</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-6 ml-10">Sale closed? Creates GitHub repo, Sanity project, Netlify site. Auto-advances to Phase 2.</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <label for="build-title" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 mb-1">Site Name</label>
              <input id="build-title" type="text" placeholder="Global Hope India"
                class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-stone-800 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-rose-300" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label for="build-slug" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 mb-1">Slug</label>
              <input id="build-slug" type="text" placeholder="global-hope-india"
                class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-stone-800 font-mono focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-rose-300" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="build-client-url" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-stone-700 mb-1">Client's Existing URL</label>
            <input id="build-client-url" type="url" placeholder="https://globalhopeindia.org"
              class="w-full border border-stone-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-stone-800 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-rose-300" />
          </div>
          <button id="bootstrap-btn"
            class="w-full bg-rose-200 hover:bg-rose-300 text-rose-900 font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed">
            Initiate Build — Phase 1
          </button>
        </div>
        <div id="bootstrap-status" class="hidden mt-5">
          <div id="bootstrap-spinner" class="hidden flex items-center gap-3 text-stone-600 text-sm">
            <svg class="animate-spin h-4 w-4 shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle class="opacity-25" cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"></circle><path class="opacity-75" fill="currentColor" d="M4 12a8 8 0 018-8v8z"></path></svg>
            <span>Creating infrastructure — GitHub, Sanity, Netlify… (~2 min)</span>
          </div>
          <div id="bootstrap-result" class="hidden p-5 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl space-y-3">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-green-800">Phase 1 complete — auto-advanced to Phase 2.</p>
            <div id="bootstrap-links" class="space-y-1.5"></div>
            <p class="text-xs text-stone-500">Next: <code class="bg-stone-100 px-1 rounded">cd ~/Sites/<span id="bootstrap-slug-echo"></span> && claude</code> — start Phase 2 (Content + CSS Extraction).</p>
          </div>
          <div id="bootstrap-error" class="hidden p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-red-800 mb-1">Error</p>
            <p id="bootstrap-error-text" class="text-sm text-red-700 font-mono whitespace-pre-wrap"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2: Content + CSS Extraction -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-rose-200 p-8 mb-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-rose-700 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">2</span>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Phase 2 — Content + CSS Extraction</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-4 ml-10">Crawl the original site and extract everything needed to replicate it — content AND styling.</p>
        <div class="ml-10 space-y-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-2">Step 1 — Crawl all pages</p>
            <ul class="text-stone-500 text-xs space-y-1 ml-3">
              <li>&bull; Fetch every page (follow nav links, sitemap, internal links)</li>
              <li>&bull; Save per page: headings, body text, CTAs, nav structure, footer, images, media</li>
              <li>&bull; Document page inventory with URL map</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-2">Step 2 — Extract complete CSS at two viewports</p>
            <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs mb-2">Use Playwright to load each page and read <code class="bg-stone-100 px-1 rounded">getComputedStyle()</code> at <strong>desktop (1280px)</strong> and <strong>mobile (375px)</strong>. Extract:</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-xs">
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2"><strong class="text-stone-700">Colors:</strong> <span class="text-stone-500">primary, secondary, accent, bg, text, link, hover, border, button, footer</span></div>
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2"><strong class="text-stone-700">Fonts:</strong> <span class="text-stone-500">font-family for headings, body, nav, buttons (exact stack)</span></div>
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2"><strong class="text-stone-700">Typography:</strong> <span class="text-stone-500">font-size, weight, line-height, letter-spacing per element</span></div>
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2"><strong class="text-stone-700">Spacing:</strong> <span class="text-stone-500">padding, margin, max-width on sections, containers, cards</span></div>
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2"><strong class="text-stone-700">Decorations:</strong> <span class="text-stone-500">border-radius, box-shadow, transitions</span></div>
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2"><strong class="text-stone-700">Navigation:</strong> <span class="text-stone-500">desktop type (horizontal/dropdowns), mobile type (hamburger/slide-out)</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-2">Step 3 — Catalog all media</p>
            <ul class="text-stone-500 text-xs space-y-1 ml-3">
              <li>&bull; Download all images to <code class="bg-stone-100 px-1 rounded">/tmp/&lt;slug&gt;-images/</code> (NOT in the repo)</li>
              <li>&bull; Images &rarr; <strong>Sanity</strong> (client uploads via Studio, auto-optimized CDN)</li>
              <li>&bull; Audio &rarr; <strong>R2</strong> (Kevin uploads manually)</li>
              <li>&bull; Video &rarr; <strong>YouTube iframe</strong> (never &lt;video&gt; tag)</li>
              <li>&bull; <strong>Nothing goes in the Git repo</strong></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-2">Output files (all in <code class="bg-stone-100 px-1 rounded">content/</code>)</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-xs">
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2 font-mono">site-inventory.md <span class="font-sans text-stone-400">— URL map</span></div>
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2 font-mono">design-tokens.md <span class="font-sans text-stone-400">— complete CSS</span></div>
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2 font-mono">images.md <span class="font-sans text-stone-400">— image catalog + destinations</span></div>
              <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded p-2 font-mono">pages/*.md <span class="font-sans text-stone-400">— one file per page</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-green-800 mb-1">Done? Verify before advancing:</p>
            <ul class="text-green-700 text-xs space-y-0.5 ml-3">
              <li>&bull; <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">design-tokens.md</code> has ALL sections (Colors, Typography Desktop + Mobile, Spacing Desktop + Mobile, Decorations, Navigation)</li>
              <li>&bull; <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">pages/*.md</code> count matches page count in <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">site-inventory.md</code></li>
              <li>&bull; Every image cataloged in <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">images.md</code> with Sanity/R2 destination</li>
              <li>&bull; No TODO, TBD, or FIXME in any content file</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-green-600 text-xs mt-2">Then click <strong>Mark Phase Complete &amp; Advance</strong> in the Phase Tracker above.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3: Design + Build -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-rose-200 p-8 mb-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-rose-700 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">3</span>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Phase 3 — Design + Build</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-rose-600 bg-rose-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Stitch MCP</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-4 ml-10">Design the site in Stitch BEFORE writing Astro code. Verify designs match the original, then build.</p>
        <div class="ml-10 space-y-4">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3">
            <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-rose-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
              <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">1. Create Stitch project</p>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs"><code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">mcp__stitch__create_project</code> — title matches site name</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-rose-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
              <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">2. Create design system from extracted CSS</p>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs"><code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">mcp__stitch__create_design_system</code> — colors, fonts, roundness from <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">design-tokens.md</code>. Paste full tokens file as designMd.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-rose-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
              <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">3. Generate screens for every page</p>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs"><code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">mcp__stitch__generate_screen_from_text</code> — desktop + mobile, using content from <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">pages/*.md</code>. Faithful to original layout.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-rose-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
              <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">4. Apply design system + verify against original</p>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs"><code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">mcp__stitch__apply_design_system</code>. Compare Stitch screens against the original site — layout, colors, fonts, spacing should match. Fix with <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">mcp__stitch__edit_screens</code> if needed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-rose-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
              <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">5. Add real fonts</p>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs">Google Fonts &rarr; add <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">&lt;link&gt;</code> in Layout.astro. Use the REAL fonts from <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">design-tokens.md</code>, not Stitch substitutes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-rose-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
              <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">6. Write <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">global.css</code> from design tokens FIRST</p>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs">Every color, font, spacing, decoration as CSS variables. Include mobile overrides. <strong>Write this before building any pages.</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 border-l-4 border-rose-600 px-4 py-3 rounded-r">
              <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-1">7. Build Astro pages from Stitch designs</p>
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-xs">Use ONLY design token CSS variables — no hardcoded hex, no inline styles. Images via Sanity <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">urlFor()</code>. Hero: <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">min-h-[420px] md:min-h-[65vh]</code> (never vh alone on mobile).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-3">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-green-800 mb-1">Done? Verify before advancing:</p>
            <ul class="text-green-700 text-xs space-y-0.5 ml-3">
              <li>&bull; <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">global.css</code> has all tokens from <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">design-tokens.md</code></li>
              <li>&bull; Every page from <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">site-inventory.md</code> is built</li>
              <li>&bull; No hardcoded hex values or inline styles in .astro files</li>
              <li>&bull; <code class="bg-white px-1 rounded">npm run build</code> succeeds</li>
              <li>&bull; Compare homepage + 2 key pages against original — layout and styling match</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-green-600 text-xs mt-2">Then click <strong>Mark Phase Complete &amp; Advance</strong> in the Phase Tracker above.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 4: Wire Sanity CMS -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-rose-200 p-8 mb-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-1">
          <span class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-rose-700 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">4</span>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Phase 4 — Wire Sanity CMS</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-10 space-y-4 mt-4">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-2">What goes in Sanity vs stays static?</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-xs">
              <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-3">
                <p class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-1">Always Sanity (client edits)</p>
                <ul class="text-green-700 space-y-0.5 ml-2">
                  <li>&bull; Blog posts</li>
                  <li>&bull; Team members / bios</li>
                  <li>&bull; Testimonials</li>
                  <li>&bull; Events / calendar</li>
                  <li>&bull; Products / services catalog</li>
                  <li>&bull; FAQs</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-stone-50 border border-stone-200 rounded-lg p-3">
                <p class="font-bold text-stone-700 mb-1">Always static (developer)</p>
                <ul class="text-stone-500 space-y-0.5 ml-2">
                  <li>&bull; Legal pages (privacy, terms)</li>
                  <li>&bull; Page structure / layout</li>
                  <li>&bull; Navigation order</li>
                  <li>&bull; Footer structure</li>
                  <li>&bull; JSON-LD structured data</li>
                  <li>&bull; Component logic</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-amber-700 text-xs mt-2 font-semibold">Service descriptions, about page copy, pricing &rarr; use your judgment. If unsure, keep static — it can be moved to Sanity later.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-stone-700 text-sm mb-2">Steps</p>
            <ul class="text-stone-500 text-xs space-y-1 ml-3">
              <li>&bull; Upload all images from <code class="bg-stone-100 px-1 rounded">/tmp/&lt;slug&gt;-images/</code> to Sanity</li>
              <li>&bull; Wire image references using <code class="bg-stone-100 px-1 rounded">urlFor()</code> helper</li>
              <li>&bull; Define Sanity schemas based on decisions above</li>
